quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Reenee e julЙ—e Й—en, e julde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖҙЖҙiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕӢgol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri. ko goongofawiiЙ—o gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali Й“en njaltunooЙ“e e galleeji mu'un, kamЙ“e ko Й“e guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani Й“e: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti Й“e? Pellet Alla ko Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on Гұawloowo Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e? Alla No ЖҒiЙ—ttina Himo YaГұГұa, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-Й—on"
